snippet.title: Paradox: A Rusty Lake Film | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
When the infamous detective Dale Vandermeer wakes up in an ominous room without any recollection of his past, he soon finds himself part of a bizarre game orchestrated by an old foe as he must solve increasingly challenging puzzles to escape the room and recover his memories. 

Paradox: A Rusty Lake Film is Coming September 20th on YouTube and Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/909090/Paradox_A_Rusty_Lake_Film/! 
IMDB: https://www.imdb.com/title/tt8371922/

Cube Escape Paradox will be released on the same day as the film! Pre-Order now
iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1372021096
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.RustyLake.CubeEscapeParadox
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/909080/Cube_Escape_Paradox/
http://www.rustylakeparadox.com

#RustyLakeParadox

Written & Directed by: Sean van Leijenhorst / https://www.youtube.com/user/SseanSvL

Starring:
David Bowles as Dale Vandermeer
Elena Kejvalová as Laura Vanderboom
Bob Rafferty as the voice of Mr. Crow

Produced by: Steve Reverand and Martin Raiman (The LAB)
Executive producers: Robin Ras and Maarten Looise (Rusty Lake)
Director of Photography: Cédric Larvoire
Production Design: Jitka Sivrova
On-Set Art Director and Costume Designer: Jennifer Margaret Bailey
Music Composed by: Victor Butzelaar
Assistant to producers: Ivana Petrzelova
Gaffer: Colin Wenger
1st Assistant Camera: Nicole Goode
2nd Assistant Camera Unit A: Sakib Nazmus
2nd Assistant Camera Unit B: Adèle Perrin
Make-up Artist: Iveta Duong
Assistant Art Direction: Jacopo Giulini
Visual Effects by : David Havel and Lukasz Krawczyk
Sound Design and Sound Mix by: Vojtech Zavadil

Trailer Credits:
Edit: Sean van Leijenhorst
Music by: Victor Butzelaar
Voice-over: Bob Rafferty

A Co Production of Rusty Lake (http://www.rustylake.com) and The LAB (http://www.thelabstudios.net)

Like and follow: 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/rustylakecom 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/rustylakecom 
Instagram: https://instagram.com/rustylakecom/ 
And subscribe to our mailing list: http://eepurl.com/bhphw1
